{"tid":1337943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大批防暴警急調往西環增援 中聯辦內防暴盾牌戒備","createTime":"2019-07-21T11:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T12:20:54.000Z","uid":51620,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"50176f4e4364084db14c0b4b03d1f3700527dc5c","tid":1337943,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:36:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190721&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59847697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190721%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59847697&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTeckpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=1e818aad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190721%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59847697&h=0b04531a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190721&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59847697</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bc96c76081f9994e23ff59a4ff7824d08b520d","tid":1337943,"uid":51620,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"大批示威者今午在灣仔「結束」遊行後化整為零，一路向西走，由金鐘、中環走到西區，部份人更在中聯辦外集結，甚至向中聯辦擲蛋，沿途警察一度恍知「不知所終」。但消息稱，這是反擊的前奏．駐守九龍區的大批防暴警察正奉召經西隧往西環增援。"},{"pid":"96159a02aa3ebf1b42889d57929b589f161f6771","tid":1337943,"uid":51620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:37:13.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》記者又發現，不少機動部隊或防暴警，原早已在警總及政總內準備好全副武裝戒備，蓄勢待發。其中在添美道政府總部外的近百個巨型水馬形成的防線之內，記者估計即有數以百計的警察防守。他們以機動部隊警員為主，但亦有不少便衣探員。他們除了有頭盔及警棍等標準裝備後，亦配備了小圓盾或長方形大盾、大型胡椒水等，可作驅散人群之用。部分警員更穿上俗稱「鐵甲威龍」的防暴高保護裝備，包括護膝、護手套等，配合長方形大盾，如臨大敵。"},{"pid":"c9ecdb238d608ec63c11126bc365a5df89570bdf","tid":1337943,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"宜家出緊去嘅人注意！買多幾張15.5車飛俾前線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1337783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1337783</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"635de951f4a29230c0572c5fc2b4b0fbe952e20e","tid":1337943,"uid":51620,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:37:27.000Z","msg":"但由於示威者不斷向西移，暫未有衝擊警總或政總，機動部隊防暴警裝備暫「無用武之地」。至傍晚近7時，中聯辦外開始聚集大量示威者，有人甚至向中聯辦擲雞蛋。據記者所見，現場未見有大量警察佈防，但中聯辦外有擺放多個鐵馬作防備，中聯辦已接上鐵閘加強防備，中聯辦內的保安人員均已戴上頭盔，更配備了有「防暴」字樣的長盾牌。"},{"pid":"f0a07f86cace4c173891281694be44ea4d144f8d","tid":1337943,"uid":124245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:37:35.000Z","msg":"幫推1"},{"pid":"bf063f385aa1e710eeff6795477857012625c5a6","tid":1337943,"uid":51620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:37:43.000Z","msg":"至傍晚，部份在政總水馬陣內的機動部隊警員忙於吃飯盒先行「醫肚」，為晚上可能出現的衝突做好準備。"},{"pid":"746f90294c4f7c6695235171c9af2eb910e6f779","tid":1337943,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"入面果班保安黎 D犬應該有排都未到"},{"pid":"0c2157909bbcfd0fb337587ebbe9656e379a7e46","tid":1337943,"uid":124245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:38:34.000Z","msg":"幫推2"},{"pid":"aa4c46d8a83c79c6cec9068af4c3fc74606dd92c","tid":1337943,"uid":124245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:38:47.000Z","msg":"幫推3"},{"pid":"6599644f96b49a117bf95a53e46ec20f608afc1f","tid":1337943,"uid":124245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"幫推4"},{"pid":"87f8d1e9877b67507ef1a5c02c0affebbfbdd2df","tid":1337943,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:39:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f000f